                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="p-6 bg-[#121218] border border-white/8 rounded-2xl hover:border-purple-500/20 transition-all group"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-500/20 to-purple-500/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
                        >
                            🎨
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2">
                            Stunning Design
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-[#7a7a82] leading-relaxed">
                            Modern, responsive layouts with animations,
                            gradients, and professional aesthetics
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="p-6 bg-[#121218] border border-white/8 rounded-2xl hover:border-purple-500/20 transition-all group"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/20 to-cyan-500/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
                        >
                            💻
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2">
                            Production-Ready Code
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-[#7a7a82] leading-relaxed">
                            Clean, maintainable full-stack code you can
                            customize and deploy immediately
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="p-6 bg-[#121218] border border-white/8 rounded-2xl hover:border-purple-500/20 transition-all group"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500/20 to-emerald-500/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
                        >
                            🤖
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2">
                            9 AI Models
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-[#7a7a82] leading-relaxed">
                            Choose from GPT-5.2, Claude 4.5, Gemini, DeepSeek,
                            and more powerful models
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="p-6 bg-[#121218] border border-white/8 rounded-2xl hover:border-purple-500/20 transition-all group"
                    >
